snippet.title: Viewpoint (PS1) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A complete playthrough of Electronic Arts' 1995 arcade shooter for the Sony PlayStation, Viewpoint, ported from the 1992 SNK Neo Geo game of the same name.

Played through on the normal difficulty level. Given how extreme the difficulty level is, it seems a bit absurd that there are another couple difficulty levels above it. 

The remixed music is pretty amazing in this version, though :)

____
No cheats were used during the recording of this video.
